<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA3">
<l>vāḻāṭ paṭṭuniṉ ṟīruḷḷī rēlvantu maṇṇu maṇamuṅkoṇmiṉ</l>
<l>kūḻāṭ paṭṭuniṉ ṟīrkaḷai yeṅkaṭ kuḻuviṉiṟ pukutaloṭṭō</l>
<l>mēḻāṭ kālum paḻippilō nāṅka ḷirākkatar vāḻilaṅkai</l>
<l>pāḻā ḷākap paṭaiporu tāṉukkup pallāṇṭu kūṟutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you are permanently a life-long servant, come [and] take the dust and fragrance [of the devotees’ feet]!</l>
<l>We shall not permit the entrance of those who are slaves to food into our community.</l>
<l>For seven generations we who are without sin shall proclaim many years for him</l>
<l>who fought an army for the destruction of Lanka – where Rāvaṇa lived –[and its] men.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
